p.e:
NOTED SOME STRANGE SYMBOLS
PREVALENT IN THE HOMES OF A
FEW OF THE MORE FRIENDLY
FOLKS HERE.

CERTAINLY SIGNIFICANT, THEY
ARE LIKE NOTHING I HAVE SEEN
BACK HOME.
OR PERHAPS THAT IS MY GUT
SPEAKING, AS LOOKING AT SOME
HAS CAUSED ME BRIEF BOUTS OF
NAUSEA.


THIS LINE OF THINKING MAKES ME
PONDER THE SYMBOL ON THE
TOWN BANNER.

--A.W.
